00:17:11.000 --> 00:17:13.000
That's the kind of principle he had.

00:17:13.000 --> 00:17:18.000
And he was a big burliger, still as tall, big,

00:17:18.000 --> 00:17:21.000
and had a scholarship to play defensive end.

00:17:21.000 --> 00:17:24.000
I believe at the University of Wisconsin.

00:17:24.000 --> 00:17:33.000
And instead, he came to Hollywood, worked in the cafeteria, didn't have any scholarship, didn't play football, and joined the movement.

00:17:33.000 --> 00:17:40.000
So there was a mixture of young people at Hollywood.

00:17:40.000 --> 00:17:46.000
Some of them from the deep south, La Vaughan, I never forget him.

00:17:46.000 --> 00:17:50.000
He was in a room next door to me.

00:17:50.000 --> 00:17:52.000
